    dc:description "FIGURES 41–51. Sobarocephala icmbio sp. nov. Paratype ♂. 41, head, frontal view; 42, habitus, dorsal view; 43, habitus, lateral view; 44, sternites and terminalia, ventral view; 45, sternites 6–8, ventral view; 46, epandrium, cerci and surstyli, dorsal view; 47, terminalia, ventral view, subepandrial sclerite outlined; 48, terminalia, lateral view; 49, ejaculatory apodeme, lateral view; 50, hypandrial complex, lateral view; 51, holotype labels. Abbreviations: basiph = basiphallus; cer = cercus; distph = distiphallus; ej apod = ejaculatory apodeme; epand = epandrium; epiph = epiphallus; hypd = hypandrium; paraph = paraphallus; phapod = phalapodeme; pgt = postgonite; pregt = pregonite; st = sternite; subepand scl = subepandrial sclerite; sur = surstylus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8430684/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8430686>
    dc:description "FIGURES 52–61. Sobarocephala icmbio sp. nov. Paratype ♀. 52, head, frontal view; 53, habitus, dorsal view; 54, habitus, lateral view; 55, basal sternites, ventral view; 56, distal sternites, ventral view; 57, apex of abdomen, lateral view; 58, genital chamber and sternite 8, ventral view; 59, spermatheca; 60, cluster of eggs, lateral view; 61, egg, anterior view, margin outlined. Abbreviations. cerc = cercus; gen ch = genital chamber; st = sternite; t = tergite." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8430686/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

